import { Router } from "express";

const routes = Router

routes.get('/tasks')

routes.get('/tasks/count')

routes.get('/tasks/:id')

routes.post('/tasks')

routes.put('/tasks/:id')

routes.delete('/tasks/:id')

export default routes

import { Router } from "express";
import { getTask } from "../controllers/index.controller";



const routes = Router

routes.get('/tasks', getTask)

routes.get('/tasks/count')

routes.get('/tasks/:id')

routes.post('/tasks')

routes.put('/tasks/:id')

routes.delete('/tasks/:id')

export default routes
